identifier: FlyByWireSASMode
abstract: >-
  Adds a new "fly by wire" SAS mode. When enabled, pitch and yaw inputs don't
  control the vessel directly anymore, but instead control the position of a
  custom navball direction marker that the SAS will follow automatically.
